When creating a new page in this project:

Scaffold a new folder inside /pages/ using the page slug.

Create index.html using /docs/templates/NEW_PAGE_INDEX_TEMPLATE.html.

Create spec.md using /docs/templates/NEW_PAGE_TEMPLATE.md.

Validate slug against GLOBAL_SITE_RULES.md.

Validate keyword cluster against GLOBAL_SEO_STRATEGY.md.

Do not allow page creation without a spec.md file.

Ensure required internal linking rules are satisfied.

Output a checklist including:

slug

H1

meta title

meta description

internal links

image files required

Always enforce page-pod structure:
Each page must contain:

index.html

spec.md

images/ directory

Never create flat .html files at root.